title: hobbies
text:
I am proficient in cooking.



I like cooking because I enjoed the creation of different flavors using simple ingredients. Also, cooking on my own allows me to keep fit by following a whole-food based diet. I like the fresh taste of baby broccoli and avacado.


I am a beginner in rock climbing.



I like rock climbing because it is fulfilling and challenges me physically and mentally.


I have been learning photography for one year.



I like photography because it is a great way to preserve exciting momories during travelling. Whenever I look back at them, I can immediate recall the feelings I had during the trip.
